es-stagehand-ui-label-explanation = [bold]Stagehands[/bold] are a unique [italic]out-of-character[/italic] role in Ephemeral Space.

    As a stagehand, your job is to create [italic]interest, conflict, and excitement[/italic] for the players on board the station.
    To accomplish this, you'll have access to a variety of votable options to affect the people on-station with.
    Additionally, you'll also be able to observe the station itself, seeing people's actions, masks, and objectives.

    {""}[color=red][bold]Warning:[/bold] Once you become a stagehand, you will be [bold]unable to return[/bold] to the theater for the remainder of the round![/color]
